uientry.unicode: Toggle Bombardment||Once active, left click on the area you wish to bombard
Focused support||Bombards a smaller area, but more accurately
uientry.s:
dofile "data/ui/templates/template.fe_button_standard.lua"
local this = UIComponent(Address)
function OnClickUp() UIComponent(this:Parent()):LuaCall("Notify", Component.Messages.StateChange, this:CurrentState(), Address) end

uientry.unicode: Area support||Covers a wider area than focused support, but is less accurate
uientry.s:
